flowchart TB
    TG[Telegram Group\nContent Posting Request] --> ROUTER[poster-router\nThin intake + triage]

    ROUTER -->|event announcement / signup post| EVENTS[events-poster\nPriority 1]
    ROUTER -->|route / roadbook / route page| ROUTES[routes-poster\nPriority 2]
    ROUTER -->|recap / promo / media post| MEDIA[media-poster\nPriority 3]
    ROUTER -->|knowledge / training / nutrition| KNOWLEDGE[knowledge-poster\nPriority 4]

    EVENTS --> REPO[(ACC Repo)]
    ROUTES --> REPO
    MEDIA --> REPO
    KNOWLEDGE --> REPO

    REPO --> SITE[Across CC Site\nVercel Rendered]
